{
  "stem": "13851.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was just-- we knew the problem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as I told you before, nobody could imagine what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How'd it start changing my life?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I felt very-- that we have no help, we're helpless.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That makes you feel like you can-- you're very getting, like, paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can't do free things what you want to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You want to work, you want to go to a movie, you want to go out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can't do that anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you have to be like a ghetto, they start to make.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to live all in the same place, same streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it-- it was terrible feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just helpless feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was a ghetto in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- what the-- where we lived, at the address I told you, the ghetto was there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was close to the market, and a lot of Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But people lived out of-- out of the ghetto had to move in into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people had to move with other families, because no place to stay, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the ghetto [? already. ?] They made this in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They surrounded it with, like, signs, 'This is the ghetto,' like the Gentiles shouldn't go in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you have other families at that time, then, move in with you?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, there's-- yeah, there was other people in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time already, Jewish people from close to the border of Germany that they already sent out, when the Jewish people-- when the Germans came in close to the German border, the Jewish people came to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember exactly there was [INAUDIBLE] a place, Konin, K-O-N-I-N, and that's around [?",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
